{"tid":1951015,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好羨慕人哋有個咁嘅老母","createTime":"2020-03-30T16:46:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-31T11:51:36.000Z","uid":292622,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5d83d0ec23323c1443c63a03132670db4c8dbafe","tid":1951015,"uid":292622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T16:46:41.000Z","msg":"【2.24葵涌邨事件專訪】<br />\n<br />\n香港反送中運動持續將近9個月。社會上有極度的撕裂及對峙，無論是政府對市民，警察對市民，或是市民對市民，都有嚴重的對立。而不少家庭因政治運動而導致之間關係緊張，亦出現不少矛盾和紛爭。本報聯絡到於2月24日其中一名被捕人士的母親(下稱A太太)並進行訪問。<br />\n<br />\nA太太從旁人得知自己的兒子於2月24日以涉嫌刑事毀壞罪被拘捕。在兒子被羈留的48小時期間，她表示不想再理會他，但事實上內心是非常擔心，並徹夜難以入睡。她坦言：「很擔心兒子會在警署中受到&ldquo;特別&rdquo;的對待。」而在兩天過後，警方因沒有足夠證據而無條件釋放他。A太太表示他的兒子被捕後，她對兒子的想法完全轉變了。//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/114449850191762/posts/122301012739979/?d=n&amp;substory_index=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F114449850191762%2Fposts%2F122301012739979%2F%3Fd%3Dn%26substory_index%3D0&d=C7qEe2dSMr%2BabA5wG5krtHRNzM9MViFDfs2457H6WAQ%3D&h=6239ba50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/114449850191762/posts/122301012739979/?d=n&amp;substory_index=0</a>"},{"pid":"051427ceaaf32b57b2a0df0e6fcfe93dc579cded","tid":1951015,"uid":292622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T16:49:09.000Z","msg":"我都希望自己有咁嘅老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10697144be636901e7789b93d7c0ca742ecbe595","tid":1951015,"uid":110749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T16:53:48.000Z","msg":"我都好撚想有個咁既老母"},{"pid":"45a7862d696ba16352fae2d713bbf53c80c6b621","tid":1951015,"uid":199415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T16:59:08.000Z","msg":"我都好想"},{"pid":"89820bd50474cf9475b940ddf7ebfb9d0ca2dec7","tid":1951015,"uid":199415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T16:59:39.000Z","msg":"唉"},{"pid":"ea072b98c5fe71114c08b3a6ce058cd46ed9a8a0","tid":1951015,"uid":161545,"lik